          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Indigenous land rights & legal empowerment for justice.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-cloud-sun text-3xl mb-4 text-orange-400"></i>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Climate-Resilient</h4>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Climate-resilient agriculture practices for a better future.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-person-dress text-3xl mb-4 text-orange-400"></i>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Women Empowerment</h4>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Economic and social upliftment for women & adolescent girls.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white/10 p-6 rounded-xl backdrop-blur-sm">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake-simple text-3xl mb-4 text-orange-400"></i>
          <h4 class="font-bold text-xl mb-2">Peacebuilding</h4>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80">Promoting social cohesion and harmony in society.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

