            <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-2xl"></i>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-3">Safeguarding & PSEA</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">Maintaining a zero-tolerance approach toward exploitation, abuse, and harassment to ensure a safe environment for all.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-8 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 bg-white">
